snippet.textDisplay:
🙏🏻Regarding the non inclusion of V's name under the artist section of Sweet Night in YouTube.

To whoever it may concern,
While listening to Sweet Night on YouTube today, some of us noticed that Vlending has not
mentioned "V" as the artist and original owner of the song in the descriptions. This
unprofessional mistake of the channel will give him absolutely no YouTube points for the
Billboard charts, despite the video being in the ‘Music’ category. Now that only 2 days have
been left for the tracking week for Hot100 to get over and this mistake can clearly affect the
charting possibility of Sweet Night in Hot100 Billboard Charts, we humbly request you to rectify
this mistake and devise a solution to this problem within the shortest time possible. Kim
Taehyung aka BTS' V has worked tirelessly and very hard for this song, and we want his hard
work to be acknowledged so please respect that fact and adress this issue with immediate
action. We expect your full compensation in this regard.
